{{Infobox music festival | name = Down The Rabbit Hole | image = Down The Rabbit Hole 2016.jpg | image_size = | alt = | caption = The Groene Heuvels during Down The Rabbit Hole 2016 | genre = | dates = June | location = [[Ewijk]], The Netherlands | years_active = 2014 – | founders = | attendance = | capacity = | website = [http://downtherabbithole.nl/ downtherabbithole.nl] | organizer = [[Mojo Concerts]] }}
'''Down The Rabbit Hole''' ('''DRTH''') is a three-day [[music festival]] that takes place in the [[Groene Heuvels]] leisure area in the village of [[Ewijk]] (near [[Nijmegen]]) in the [[Netherlands]]. It was first organized in 2014 and has since been held annually late in June.
Like [[Lowlands (festival)|Lowlands]] it is organized by [[Mojo Concerts]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://go.3fm.nl/festivals/nieuws-detail/5226/Down-The-Rabbit-Hole-in-recreatiegebied-bij-Nijmegen |title=Down The Rabbit Hole in recreatiegebied bij Nijmegen |language=Dutch |publisher=[[NPO 3FM]] |date=14 November 2013 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gelderlander.nl/regio/wijchen-beuningen/broertje-van-lowlands-festival-op-groene-heuvels-ewijk-down-the-rabbit-hole-1.4096919 |title=Broertje van Lowlands-festival op Groene Heuvels Ewijk: Down the Rabbit Hole |language=Dutch |publisher=[[De Gelderlander]] |date=14 November 2013 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref> and marketed as a competitor to [[Best Kept Secret (festival)|Best Kept Secret]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.volkskrant.nl/dossier-lowlands/lowlands-organisatie-komt-met-hippieesk-festival-down-the-rabbit-hole~a3544789/ |title=Lowlands-organisatie komt met hippieësk festival Down The Rabbit Hole |language=Dutch |first=Just |last=Fontein |publisher=[[de Volkskrant|Volkskrant]].nl |date=14 November 2013 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref><ref name="NRC tips">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nrc.nl/muziek/2014/06/27/nieuw-festival-down-the-rabbit-hole-tips-van-de-muziekredactie/ |title=Nieuw festival Down The Rabbit Hole: tips van de muziekredactie |language=Dutch |last=Judith |first=Laanen |publisher=[[NRC Handelsblad|NRC]] |date=27 June 2014 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref> The first edition was attended by around 10,000 people and nominated for two [[European Festival Awards]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://3voor12.vpro.nl/nieuws/2014/Down-The-Rabbit-Hole-2014/Down-The-Rabbit-Hole-wil-naar-35.000-bezoekers-met-40-jaren-plan.html |title=Down The Rabbit Hole wil "naar 35.000 bezoekers met 40-jaren plan" |language=Dutch |first=Ingmar |last=Griffioen |publisher=[[3voor12]] |date=30 June 2014 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gelderlander.nl/regio/wijchen-beuningen/down-the-rabbit-hole-ewijk-genomineerd-voor-2-awards-1.4582118 |title=Down the Rabbit Hole Ewijk genomineerd voor 2 awards |language=Dutch |publisher=[[De Gelderlander]] |date=16 October 2014 |access-date=17 November 2014}}</ref> The three main stages – "Hotot", "Fuzzy Lop", and "Teddy Widder" – are named after [[List of rabbit breeds|rabbit breeds]].<ref name="NRC tips" />
* The 2014 edition saw [[Damon Albarn]], [[The Black Keys]], and [[Foals (band)|Foals]] as headliners. * The 2015 edition had [[Damien Rice]], [[Iggy Pop]], and [[The War on Drugs (band)|The War on Drugs]] play. * In 2016 the festival was headlined by [[PJ Harvey]], [[The National (band)|The National]], and [[Anohni]]. * The 2017 edition was headlined by [[Moderat]], [[Fleet Foxes]], and [[Oscar and the Wolf]]. * In 2018 [[Queens of the Stone Age]], [[Anderson Paak|Anderson .Paak & The Free Nationals]], and [[Nick Cave & The Bad Seeds]] headlined the festival.
