==Forced to Eat Feces==

==="Operation" against Kurdish village===
{{Expand section|date=July 2011}}
The Yeşilyurt village of Cizre district was besieged by gendarmeries on January 14–15, 1989. Commander Cafer Tayyar Çağlayan and his soldiers made villagers eat feces.

Kamil Müştak (died December 13, 2007)
